Package: basicstats
Title: Basic summary stats by strata
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrew", "Fullerton", , "afullert@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: basicstats makes it easier for you to produce basic summary statistics (mean, median, range, and sample size) by levels of a grouping variable in a tidy, easy-to-read summary.
